      <div class="small text-muted">
        At each band level, we total micro-question weights and passed weights. If pass rate is <span class="fw-bold">>= 50%</span>, the criterion proceeds to the next band.
        If below 50%, progression stops and the criterion band is finalized at the current step rule.
      </div>
      <div class="row g-2 mt-2">${scoreCards}</div>
      <div class="mt-2 small">
